Client library for C language.
=====

=========================================
Message level conterol
=========================================
This library outputs messages including error, warning, information, and debug to
standard output or standard error.

The message output can be controlled by the environment variable 'HISTORY_GLUON_MSG_LV'.
The available levels are the following.
- DBG
- INFO
- WARN
- ERR
- CRIT
- NONE

Ex.)
$ export HISTORY_GLUON_MSG_LV=ERR
